.SH NAME
mihomoctl-cache-clear-all - Flush fakeip and DNS caches


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmihomoctl cache clear all [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Flush fakeip first, then DNS. If one cache fails, mihomoctl reports a partial failure with per-cache results.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for all


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
